window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Girl meets dragon. Girl works to befriend dragon. A large, red, dangerous dragon.</b></p> <p>Raven Alby will have to train her new ride and save the dragon’s life or die trying.</p> <p>Mix in starting at Fowler Academy as a first-year, becoming a stronger mage, and oh...people disappearing.</p> <p>It's all adding up to typical teenager stuff for a young mage.</p> <p>The first lesson Raven will learn? Don’t ever let anything come between a girl and her dragon.</p>"; 
